45
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:51,000
Zhuo Minghua
is the Master Zhuo's cousin.

46
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,318
But surely,

47
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:54,199
about Zhuo Minghua's serious crime,

48
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,480
Master Zhuo was unaware.

49
