67
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:51,000
I said,

68
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,319
move without permission,

69
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,560
you will be killed without mercy.

70
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,960
Your Majesty,

71
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,680
Master Zhuo,

72
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:02,239
Zhuo Minghua defied his superior,

73
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,240
and intended rebellion.

74
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,000
I have executed him.

75
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,439
The case of Junlai Village

76
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,360
is closed.

77
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:13,120
