78
00:03:13,121 --> 00:03:14,319
drag Zhuo Minghua out.

79
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,439
Junlai Village,

80
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:24,240
also known as Widow Village.

81
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:25,919
This case

82
