of the entire village.

83
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,839
They lived difficult lives
and were heavily oppressed.

84
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:35,680
But they tried so hard to live better.

85
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:38,400
Even when pushed
into such a desperate situation,

86
00:03:38,639 --> 00:03:40,959
they never thought of leaving this place

87
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,439
called Widow Village.

88
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:44,080
Why?

89
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,960
Because the world is vast,

90
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:50,759
