106
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,600
Your Majesty,

107
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,680
please listen to me.

108
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,759
A woman obeys her father at home,

109
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,518
